headline: Netflix Thinks It Can Reach a Trillion-Dollar Market Cap by 2030. Here's What the Math Says.
summary: Netflix's management reportedly believes it can double revenue and triple operating income by 2030.  The company is increasing prices and building out its advertising service.  The world is Netflix's (NASDAQ: NFLX) oyster.
